# Britannia Timepass Chips – Sales & Marketing Performance Dashboard

## 📊 Project Overview

Analyzed Britannia Timepass Chips sales data across 4 regions and 12 cities using Power BI and Excel.  
Built an interactive dashboard to visualize performance metrics and identify growth opportunities.

## 🛠 Tools Used

- Power BI
- Excel
- Data Modeling
- DAX (KPIs, Filters)
- Data Cleaning & Transformation

## 🔍 Key Insights

- Analyzed over ₹8M+ revenue and 500K+ units sold
- Identified top-performing cities and SKU combinations
- Tracked sales trends, category performance, and regional growth
- Created actionable visual insights using pie charts, KPIs, bar graphs, and slicers

## 📁 Files Included

- `Britannia snacks Performance analysis.pbix`: Power BI Dashboard file
- `Britannia Timpass Chips Project.docx`: Summary report & key insights
- `Britannia_Timepass_Chips_Realistic_Dataset.xlsx`: Raw dataset with regions, cities, products


